acme.short_description: This collection was created to address a trending style in today's market while adding some transitional feel by bowing the inset drawers. Use of the slats in the center of the drawer and hardware to match the slats creates a uniform design element. Slat look is carried through to the accents on the mirror as well as the beds. The panel bed uses the middle slat look of the cases to have a suited option. Cases and beds are on metal legs to modernize the collection. This collection features Sherwin-Williams finish on Poplar solids and veneers to emphasize the glued up look and accentuate the grain characteristics.
